The paper discusses natural language question answering (NLQA) and the role of external knowledge in NL understanding. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses knowledge acquisition and use in NLQA models, which could also place it in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Cybernetics (cs.CY) sub-categories.
